{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_04_01_short",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 確かな成長と違和感 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千紗と沙季が出場した、ユニットバトル決勝前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day before the unit battle finals with Chisa and Saki participating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、お疲れ様。最後の練習は終わったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki‚ good job. Are you done with the final practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、ついさっき終わったところです\n千紗は……サニピの皆さんと話してますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job to you too. We just finished a moment ago.\nChisa-chan is… talking with everyone from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……沙季も千紗も\nここ数日で一気に成長したな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so… both Saki and Chisa\nhave grown so much these past few days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "顔つきから違うし、ユニットとしての完成度も抜群だ\n一体何をしたらここまで変われるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a difference in your demeanor‚ and it''s complete as a unit.\nWhat did you guys do to change this much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "つい数日前までは、どうやったらこのユニットが\n良くなるのかずっと悩んでいたんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until just a few days ago‚ I was constantly\nworried about how to improve our unit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗に言われたんです\n「お姉ちゃんは本当は前に出たいんじゃないの？」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then Chisa-chan said to me‚\n\"Don't you honestly want to stand out?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "その上、「このままお姉ちゃんが譲るなら、私の方が\n前に出て目立っちゃうんだから」とまで言われまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ she even said‚ \"If you keep stepping back‚\nI'll be the one who stands out.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな……千紗がそんな大胆なことを言ったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm surprised… Chisa said something so bold?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}